<h1>Welcome!</h1>

<% unless Current.user.email_verified? %>
  <div class="flash flash--warning">
    ⚠️ Your email is not yet verified. Please check your inbox.
  </div>
<% end %>

<div class="card">
  <p>
    Plural Profiles is a space for plural people to create and share profiles. You can set up individual profiles with names, pronouns, avatars,
    and descriptions, and organise them into groups, however works best for you.
  </p>
  <p>
    Each profile and group gets a shareable public link you can give to
    friends, add to bios, or keep handy for introductions.
  </p>
</div>

<% profile_count = Current.user.profiles.count %>
<% group_count = Current.user.groups.count %>

<div class="card">
  <h2>At a glance</h2>

  <% if profile_count.zero? && group_count.zero? %>
    <p>
      You haven't created anything yet, and that's okay!
      Use the sidebar to add your first profile or group whenever you&rsquo;re ready.
    </p>
  <% else %>
    <p>
      You currently have
      <strong><%= pluralize(group_count, "group") %></strong>
      and
      <strong><%= pluralize(profile_count, "profile") %></strong>.
    </p>
  <% end %>
</div>
